{
  "stem": "5375.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] But whatever I will do, whatever I won't do, but I have to learn.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And life didn't go too well for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I was 13 years old, I was bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't take it no more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I ran away from this town here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father shouldn't know where my-- my whereabouts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I want to learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't want to be hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't take the hunger, and I couldn't take the sufferings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't see no future.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 1933, the economic situation was getting bad, because even here in United States, how much I understand, it wasn't so-- so good.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there, it was horribly worse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I couldn't-- just couldn't take it no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because I was going around hungry, and in wintertime, I wasn't dressed for the cold occasion, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Finally, I ran away to another town where my father won't know about it, except my mother, rest her in peace.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I let her know-- not-- my father shouldn't have known.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Should he have known where I am, he would have come.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And by my ears, he would schlep me back to go back to [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeshiva ?] to learn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I learned the trade, the fur trade there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Right away, my situation improved to 100%.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At least he gave me food to eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I learned the trade for two and a half years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With-- in the house, in the-- by my-- by my boss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, in the beginning, I had to take more care of the children and do more housework than learn trades.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in the meantime, it was food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was clothing-- he gave me clothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Poorly, but surely, better than I had before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wasn't hungry no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
